            .. code::
        
                git clone git@github.com:<username>/pockyt.git
                cd pockyt
                pip install -e .
                git checkout -b new-feature
                ...
                # do stuff
                ...
                git add .
                git commit -am 'commit msg'
                git push origin new-feature
        
        3. Submit a `pull request <https://github.com/achembarpu/pockyt/compare>`_.
        
